{"tid":1048420,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"去酒吧廁所疴尿記住唔好咁大聲。。。","createTime":"2019-03-05T15:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T18:15:37.000Z","uid":216662,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"050de67761e92a557f3ed7d97d02e62c8803230d","tid":1048420,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:36:40.000Z","msg":"是咁的～<br />\n上次同兩個fd去飲嘢，飲咗幾杯嗰兩條友就話急尿一齊去咗廁所。<br />\n唔夠一分鐘兩個fd就無啦啦打交打到出嚟，打到反曬枱掃曬啲樽落地下。<br />\n分開咗佢地就問發生咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nfd a：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母！我疴尿大聲關你撚事呀<br />\n<br />\nfd b：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未撚見過人疴尿咁撚大地，嘈撚到我疴唔出，屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n話口未完兩個又扭打起上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而我就笑到無力幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />疴尿大聲都打交真係第一次見。。。"},{"pid":"4a091d1663b06634ba483b4fe8abd99f750f1dcf","tid":1048420,"uid":3695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:37:12.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"0865c4d08a5264abca5b0c050901b4826816c6b2","tid":1048420,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a091d1663b06634ba483b4fe8abd99f750f1dcf","tid":1048420,"uid":3695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:37:12.000Z","msg":"1/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:38:06.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c928aeecccb4a801066c81561e79562082095705","tid":1048420,"uid":142351,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:39:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b6dd03e083b3f3cfb204e668fad0c299819c67c","tid":1048420,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c928aeecccb4a801066c81561e7